  "instructions": [
    "Combine white wine, sake (if using), brown sugar, and water in a saucepan and bring to a simmer over medium heat.",
    "Reduce the mixture to about 1 cup, stirring occasionally, about 10 minutes.",
    "Soak the dried cod in cold water for at least 4 hours or overnight. Drain and cut into small pieces.",
    "Heat the sesame oil in a pan over medium heat and add the cod pieces. Cook until browned and crispy, about 3-4 minutes per side.",
    "Prepare sushi rice according to package instructions. Season with rice vinegar and let cool to room temperature.",
    "Shape sushi rice into small balls and flatten slightly into nigiri shapes.",
    "Place a small piece of cod on top of each rice ball.",
    "Garnish with sesame seeds, pickled ginger, and green onions.,"
  ],
